reviews.review_text: I wanted to take a moment to share my heartfelt appreciation for the exceptional customer service I recently received at your McDonalds establishment, all thanks to the outstanding efforts of your employee, David. During my recent visit to your restaurant, I was pleasantly surprised by the level of service that David provided. From the moment I walked in, his welcoming greeting set a positive tone for my dining experience. Throughout my visit, Davids attentiveness, courtesy, and professionalism were consistently on display, making my time at McDonalds truly enjoyable. In an industry where exceptional customer service can make a significant difference, Davids dedication to going above and beyond stood out. His polite and accommodating demeanor exemplified the kind of service that keeps customers coming back. I believe that employees like David are a valuable asset to your team, and they contribute significantly to the positive image of your establishment. Please extend my sincere thanks to him for his outstanding service and for making my visit memorable. I look forward to returning to your McDonalds location in the future, knowing that I can expect the same level of excellence in customer service. Thank you for maintaining such high standards and for having exceptional employees like David.

I love this McDonalds!!  Im a tow truck driver and so I have to eat on the fly.  This McDonalds is fast and efficient.  They always, always ask if Im collecting points on the App which I love because I do.  Most other locations I frequent like Scottsdale or Newton never ask.  Im addicted to their coffee Fraps. I usually buy at least 3 a day.  The store is always super clean. The staff there are super friendly and helpful especially the manager, Bal, who I often see helping out at the drive thru window.

I generally use the drive thru. The food is what you expect from a McDonalds. I gave 4 stars for service because I almost always get asked to pull around to the side to wait for my order. I have spent 10 minutes at the side. I understand things happen but this is a regular occurrence.
Sim ran and staff are absolutely amazing and wonderful. Always accurate, and always kind! Its a pleasure to come here!
Excellent quick service. But the wrap should have been more grilled!

Food was better than the other McDonalds I have tried in the area. Customer service was really good and service was fast. Would love to visit again whenever got a chance to as food quality is really better than other locations i have tried.

We go thru the drive thru at least twice to three times a day . The crew is so awesome and treat us like family. We get ice coffees , our muffins. Done perfectly. Thank you to our lady millionaire and little mouse! All of you! We appreciate all you do .
Nice people and fast service. Will be eating there again.
I mostly goes in morning. Great experience. Staff is cooperative. Food

I don t know what changed here but the service and staff improved so much. It s nice to finally get great friendly service when I am getting food. There was a mishap with my tea but honestly they were super nice I didn t even care. If Tim Hortons messes up your order they give you attitude and roll their eyes at you.

Really good place to eat. I have been there very often. Today at about 5:30pm i went in the drive thru and a brown girl took my order and i think her name was balveer or dalveer something like that. She took my order and told me to park. Her way of talking to me was very nice and polite. She had a great smile on her face while she was talking to me. She said that I have dropped fresh food for you so could you please pull around the corner. I really appreciate that she gave me fresh food and especially her way of taking order was awesome. All staff is good and friendly.
Great food and awesome people. Coffee is always fresh and hot. What more could I ask for.

Mmmm I love chicken nuggets, happy meals , fries no salt & regular chicken BuRG, BBQ sauce, mchicken burg sauce in a hot fudge Sunday lid, with Adam Berry berry Legendary pie and vanilla ice cream! What happened to twist cones? Says Kerri Baldeep CHOHAN? Maybe they are at jacques in a box with Surrey jack peeps

My kids decide to throw their jacket in the air and it of course got stuck out of reach on the awning. The staff was awesome and helped me get it down. They are all friendly with great customer service skills.

Great McDonalds Was here during their 50th anniversary and was impressed by the good service. With McDonalds, expectations are pretty low, but here the manager was friendly and helpful, the store was clean and even though it was really busy, I got served pretty quickly. Pleasantly surprised!

Always come to this McDonalds because I know theyll make my food hot and right the first time. Dont know about all these other reviews but Im always driving a large vehicle that wont fit in the drivethru and theyve always brought it out to me without attitude. Favorite McDonalds by far.

Amazing service, with the busy morning hours theyre FAST.. And you got you order exactly the way you want. And the best thing is that the Friendly staff.. Thank you guys for your hot coffee every morning

Called ahead with a big order for my guys who are working today.and was there 5 minutes later as our location is just behind the restaurant. Food was hot fresh and put together very quickly. Great Job !!!!!
